    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to PyCairo for Python2 Module</title>

      <para>
        This version of
        PyCairo provides <application>Python2</application> bindings to
        <application>Cairo</application>.
      </para>

      &lfs110a_checked;
      <!-- Does not use gcc -->

